<h4>Sales &amp; Customer Service Training</h4>
<p>Our Everything DiSC&reg;&nbsp;Sales&nbsp;programme teaches sales people how to connect better with their customers. Everything DiSC Sales&nbsp;increases sales effectiveness using the power of DiSC. Salespeople learn to communicate better and improve their sales relationships.</p>
<p>Tapping into the power of this DiSC&reg;-based training solution helps sales professionals effectively recognise and adapt to their customers&rsquo; unique buying styles&mdash;and close more sales.</p>
<p>This training programme puts the power of the Everything DiSC&reg; model into the hands of salespeople and provides a dynamic tool to help them discover new strategies for stretching beyond their natural preferences to make the selling process more productive and successful.</p>
<h5>Learner Take-Aways&nbsp;</h5>
<ul>
<li>Discover their own DiSC&reg;&nbsp;style: recognise the priorities, personal strengths, and challenges that shape their sales interactions with others</li>
<li>Explore other styles: &nbsp;understand the differences and similarities among DiSC buying styles, learn to recognise the behaviours unique to each style, and identify new ways to find common ground with all types of customers</li>
<li>Create a plan of action to get more out of the sales process&mdash;and deliver better bottom line results&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
